"Second puzzle in two weeks" 

Would those two puzzles both have been on Thursday? That is the day of the week designated for "tricky" puzzles at the NYT. If you truly find them too frustrating to enjoy, perhaps just skip that day of the week (or exit early). I did exactly that for at least a year when I first started solving regularly!

